main concept, planning, design, code: emberling

thanks to abyssonym and everyone who contributed to Beyond Chaos for creating
something that, in so many ways, is ALMOST something I really want to play
but instead is something I don't want to play, inspiring me to work to
close that gap. also, thanks for your program basically teaching me how to
python.

thanks to Gi Nattak for your music insertion and creation tutorials
thanks to Gi Nattak and madsiur and everyone who contributed to the excellent
docs on ff6hacking.com

